  m_text: "After countless failed experiments, the robot finally broke free from
    the laboratory.\r\n\rBehind the steel walls, it was once only a test subject.\r\nBut
    through danger, traps, and endless corridors, it found something greater than
    survival:\r\n\rFreedom.\r\n\rAlthough the lab has been escaped, the outside world
    is still unknown.\r\nThis is not the end of the robot's story.\r\nIt is the beginning
    of a new journey."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
